data.text:
So I finally started using webstagram and its so much easier to follow threads and post comments. I'm all thumbs on the iphone keyboard plus the stability issue of the app has been killing me this past week.
So Webstagram is an awesome way to interact with your IG feed but I also found this site called http://instagram.heroku.com/  It's super simple just lays the photos out in tiles.  It's a great way to send your album to friends or family not on IG.  Check it out!
Your photos look beautiful laid out like that. (I mean, they're beautiful on their own too but even lovelier when you see them all at once.)
